<td tEditID="c1r1" style=" background-color:#FFFFFF; bEditID:r3st1; color:#000000; bLabel:main; font-size:12pt; font-family:arial;" aEditID="c1r1" locked="0" >
<![CDATA[<div style="background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><div style=""><div style=""><div style=""><div style=""><div style=""><div style=""><div style=""><div style=""><div style=""><div style=""><div style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif;"><font face="arial" style="font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt;">Hi {!Contact.FirstName},<br></font><span style="font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt;"><br>Thank you for getting in touch with Kingsbridge.<br></span><br style="font-family: arial;"><font face="arial" style="font-family: arial;">We are writing to confirm that, as per your request,&nbsp;</font><b style="font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt;">we have cancelled your insurance policy&nbsp;<i>(insert policy number)</i></b><font face="arial" style="font-family: arial;">&nbsp;with Kingsbridge.</font><br style="font-family: arial;"><br style="font-family: arial;"><font face="arial" style="font-family: arial;">To confirm,&nbsp;<b>your policy was active for the period&nbsp;<i>(DDMMYYYY to DDMMYYYY)</i></b>.&nbsp;<br></font><br style="font-family: arial;"><span style="font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt;"><br><b>Cancelling your payment</b><br></span><span style="font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt;"><br>As you paid for your policy in a single payment, in the next 3 to 10 working days a pro-rata refund of&nbsp;<i>£XXX</i>&nbsp;will appear in the account from which you originally paid.<br></span><span style="font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt;"><br></span><span style="font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt;"><br><b>Making a claim</b><br></span><span style="font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt;"><br><i>(Remove mention of Professional Indemnity if policy does not include PI)&nbsp;</i>Any claims submitted for the Professional Indemnity and Goods and Tools Cover elements of the policy will not be met as these operate on a ‘claims made’ basis and therefore the policy must be live in order to respond.&nbsp;<br></span><span style="font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt;"><br>Any claims for the&nbsp;<i>(delete as appropriate)&nbsp;</i>Public Liability, Employers’ Liability, Contract Works, Own Plant and Hired in Plant elements for the time your policy was active can be notified to insurers. Please refer to your policy wording for full information.&nbsp;<br><br></span><span style="font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt;"><br><font face="arial">If you have any questions regarding the above, please do not hesitate to contact our customer service team on&nbsp;<b>01242 808740</b>.</font><br></span><span style="font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt;"><br><font face="arial">Kind regards,<br></font></span><span style="font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt;"><br>{!User.FirstName}<br></span><span style="font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt;">Customer Service Team<br></span><span style="font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt;"><br>E:&nbsp;</span><a href="mailto:customersupport@kingsbridge.co.uk" style="font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);">customersupport@kingsbridge.co.uk</a><br style="font-family: arial;"><span style="font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt;">T: 01242 808 740</span></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div>]]></td>
</tr>
